name: AllenCoPublicHealth
tweet: ACPH is hosting pediatric COVID-19 vaccine clinics on Wednesdays from 2-5p at the Lima Mall clinic site for 5-11 year olds. Please visit  https://t.co/f6J4813Tdb to make an appointment.  https://t.co/jxkspFjmt9

name: AllenCoPublicHealth
tweet: Appointments are recommended but not required and can be made at  https://t.co/4da7O3dPZ6. For assistance making appointments, please call 419-228-4636.  Flu shots can be given at the same time and will also be available to participants attending the COVID-19 vaccine clinics.  https://t.co/ceziwJNn76

name: AllenCoPublicHealth
tweet: On Tuesday, Nov. 2, 2021, the CDC recommended use of the Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 vaccine pediatric formulation for children ages 5-11, following a thorough review of the vaccine’s safety and effectiveness. The Pfizer pediatric vaccine is a 2-dose primary series, 3 weeks apart.

name: AllenCoPublicHealth
tweet: COVID-19 Vaccinations Available for Children Ages 5-11  ACPH will be offering the pediatric vaccine at special clinics held on Wednesday afternoons from 2:00 – 4:00 p.m. in the former Elder-Beerman store at the Lima Mall.
